com.aldebaran.qi.helper.proxies

Class ALMemory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aldebaran.qi.helper.ALProxy
      • com.aldebaran.qi.helper.ALMemoryHelper
        • com.aldebaran.qi.helper.proxies.ALMemory

  • public class ALMemory
extends ALMemoryHelper
    ALMemory provides a centralized memory that can be used to store and retrieve named values. It also acts as a hub for the distribution of event notifications.
    See Also:
    NAOqi APIs for ALMemory
